OL,3,C'My life was tipped upside down', says
OL,4,Cmum who suffered long Covid
OL,6,FA mother who suffered with long Covid
OL,7,Fsaid her life was "tipped upside down"
OL,8,Fin a "matter of weeks" after she was
OL,9,Fimpacted by "crippling" symptoms.
OL,11,FIt comes as the first day of the third
OL,12,Fmodule of the UK Covid-19 Inquiry
OL,13,Fbegins today (Monday, 9 September).
OL,15,FLeaders from the Health and Safety
OL,16,FExecutive and Unison are expected to
OL,17,Fgive evidence this week as the inquiry
OL,18,Flooks at the governmental and societal
OL,19,Fresponse to Covid-19 by assessing the
OL,20,Fimpact of the pandemic on how NHS
OL,21,Fservices were delivered.
