OL,3,C'My life was tipped upside down', says
OL,4,Cmum who suffered long Covid
OL,6,FKate Lloyd, from Bridgend, tested
OL,7,Fpositive for Covid-19 in 2022.
OL,9,FIt was not the first time she had
OL,10,Ftested positive for the virus, and
OL,11,Fassumed that she would spend a few
OL,12,Fdays feeling unwell, before returning
OL,13,Fto her usual fit and healthy self.
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, she recounted
OL,16,Fhow she became unwell quickly, with
OL,17,Fsymptoms persisting for weeks.
