OL,3,C'My life was tipped upside down', says
OL,4,Cmum who suffered long Covid
OL,6,FShe said: "I was hopeful that after a
OL,7,Fcouple of weeks, the symptoms would
OL,8,Fgo... but that wasn't the case. If
OL,9,Fanything, I started getting worse.
OL,11,F"The main thing was fatigue. It was
OL,12,Fquite crippling to the extent that
OL,13,Feven when I wanted to get out of bed,
OL,14,FI couldn't. In the mornings, I just
OL,15,Fcouldn't move my legs to lift them up
OL,16,Fand out of bed."
