OL,3,C'My life was tipped upside down', says
OL,4,Cmum who suffered long Covid
OL,6,FShe continued: "I had severe brain
OL,7,Ffog, I couldn't remember words for
OL,8,Fthings. Then the physical symptoms...
OL,9,Frapid heart rate every time I stood
OL,10,Fup. The GP explained that there was a
OL,11,Freason as to why I was feeling worse
OL,12,Fevery time I stood up- it was caused
OL,13,Fby something called POTS."
OL,15,FPostural Orthostatic Tachycardia
OL,16,Fsyndrome, is a condition that causes a
OL,17,Frapid increase in heart rate when
OL,18,Fstanding up from a sitting or lying
OL,19,Fposition.
