OL,3,C'My life was tipped upside down', says
OL,4,Cmum who suffered long Covid
OL,6,FShe added: "For me, that meant that my
OL,7,Fresting heart rate was going up about
OL,8,F50 beats per minute every time I went
OL,9,Ffrom sitting to standing. It made me
OL,10,Freally dizzy, chest pain and quite
OL,11,Ffrightened by it."
OL,13,FTasks that previously proved easy to
OL,14,FKate, became almost impossible.
