OL,3,C'My life was tipped upside down', says
OL,4,Cmum who suffered long Covid
OL,6,FShe explained: "Because of the brain
OL,7,Ffog and inability to use the words I
OL,8,Fwanted to use, I couldn't read out
OL,9,Floud. Which is why the significance of
OL,10,Fme reading to the children is so
OL,11,Fimportant now. I remember vividly
OL,12,Ftrying to read them a bedtime story,
OL,13,Fand I couldn't say the words out loud.
OL,14,FI was doing my dissertation for
OL,15,FUniversity at the time and I had to
OL,16,Fcancel that because I could not retain
OL,17,Fany information.
OL,19,F"It felt like my whole life was tipped
OL,20,Fupside down within a matter of weeks."
