OL,3,C'My life was tipped upside down', says
OL,4,Cmum who suffered long Covid
OL,6,FKate had previously heard of long
OL,7,Fcovid but never imagined she would be
OL,8,Fimpacted as she did not have any
OL,9,Funderlying health issues: "I'm fit and
OL,10,Fwell, very active, always on the go,
OL,11,Falways doing something. So it was very
OL,12,Fhard for me to see myself with that
OL,13,Fcondition."
OL,15,F"I had to have symptoms for 12 weeks
OL,16,Fbefore the GP would refer me to a Long
OL,17,FCovid Clinic. That's a really long
OL,18,Ftime when you're struggling."
